#compdef cargo-cmd
# Documentation: https://github.com/danreeves/cargo-cmd
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# cargo-cmd: alias shell commands in Cargo.toml under [package.metadata.commands].
# Upstream README documents no CLI flags; usage is `cargo cmd <name> [args]`.

_arguments -s -S \
  '1:command_name:_default' \
  '*::args:_default' && return 0
